Complete nucleotide sequence of jasmine virus H, a new member of the family 
Tombusviridae.

Zhuo T(1), Zhu LJ(1)(2), Lu CC(2), Jiang CY(2), Chen ZY(2)(3), Zhang G(4), Wang 
ZH(1)(5)(6), Jovel J(7), Han YH(8).

Author information:
